 Concept       Why We Used It           
header  | Top section of the page  
nav     | Navigation area          
ul      | Navigation is a list     
li      | Each navigation item     
a       | Links to pages/sections  
section | Groups related content   
h1      | Main heading of the page 
h2      | Site logo/name           
p       | Short description        
button  | Call-to-action           


